        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>10<hi rend="sup">th</hi> March&#47;54</date>.</p>
			<p>Rev. Dear Sir&#33;</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">I have much pleasure in transmitting<lb/> to you the <sic>inclosed</sic> invitation to the grand to&#45;do at<lb/> our school on <date>Thursday 23d.</date> Inst&#59; and I am authorised<lb/> by the Directors to say that they consider it their pleasing<lb/> duty to bear the <sic>expence</sic> attending your visit to our city<lb/> on this occasion.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">In reply to your esteemed Letter I fully appreciate<lb/> the kindness of your offer&#59; but if the Hospital dinner&#45;<lb/>managers did not think it worth their while to keep their<lb/> promise to the speakers&#44; I do not think it worth <hi rend="underline">my</hi> while<lb/> to leave any record of my co&#45;operation &#40;or rather of my<lb/> pliances&#41; on the occasion. The speech was a good one and may<lb/> serve again&#44; as &#8220;Education&#8221; is a standing dish at our public feeds.<lb/> I trust you will like the Toast<add>&#63;</add> entrusted to you.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">I am sorry there should be any misprints in <persName>Dr. Illowys</persName> Letter&#44; especially one of<lb/> which I fear our &#8220;meek and modest&#8221; brother at <placeName>Cin</placeName>&#58; will not<lb/> fail to make the most <add>Hebrew</add>. I like <persName>Dr. Ill.</persName> Letter&#59; and if you or<lb/> he have saved the portion I translated I will furnish the<lb/> remainder in the course of next week&#59; toutefore<add>&#63;</add> if it suits your<lb/> views to print it please let me know by return.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">The folks at <placeName>N. 100</placeName> unite in kind remembrance to you</p>
          <p rend="indent(6)">Very truly yours</p>
          <p rend="indent(7)"><persName role="author">M J Raphall</persName></p>
			<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Pha.</placeName></p>
